  "comment_text": {
    "sn36.12:1.3": "In Indian philosophy, the energies, breaths, or life forces (Sanskrit <i lang='pi' translate='no'>prāna</i>) in the body are connected with the sensations that are experienced moving about the body. A meditator becomes acutely aware of these when sitting still for long periods. "
  },
